&gt; &gt; &gt; -----Original Message-----
&gt; &gt; &gt; From: Vincent Massol [mailto:vmassol@...]
&gt; &gt; &gt; Sent: 13. juli 2002 12:49
&gt; &gt; &gt; To: junit@yahoogroups.com
